 Comedian <PERSON> Bob </PERSON> <PERSON> Hope </PERSON> says he's planning to build a museum and entertainment complex near here featuring mementoes from 50 years in show business. The complex will be built on 80 acres that <PERSON> Hope </PERSON> owns near <LOCATION> Walt </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Disney </LOCATION> <LOCATION> World </LOCATION>, the 85-year-old entertainer said Friday. `` It's going to have all my memorabilia and movies from the past 50 years,'' <PERSON> Hope </PERSON> told WESH-TV in an interview from <LOCATION> Los </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Angeles </LOCATION>. Details on a design and an opening date have not been worked out, <PERSON> Hope </PERSON> said.
